# Disney Solitaire Demo Video Placeholder

This file serves as a placeholder for the local Disney Solitaire gameplay video.

## Video Specifications (when implemented):
- Format: MP4 (H.264)
- Resolution: 1920x1080 (Full HD)
- Duration: 30-60 seconds
- File size: ~10-20MB (optimized for web)
- Frame rate: 30fps

## Content Suggestion:
1. Opening: Disney Solitaire logo animation
2. Gameplay: Card matching mechanics
3. Features: Disney characters and themes
4. Closing: Call-to-action to play the game

## Technical Notes:
- Add to `/videos/disney-solitaire-demo.mp4` for actual implementation
- Consider creating multiple quality versions for adaptive streaming
- Ensure video is compressed for web delivery
- Add subtitles for accessibility

## Alternative:
The component automatically falls back to an interactive image slideshow using the Disney game screenshots if video file is not available.